headline: Camden Property Trust Announces First Quarter 2025 Earnings Release and Conference Call Dates
summary: HOUSTON, April 02, 2025--Camden Property Trust (NYSE:CPT) (the "Company") announced today that its first quarter 2025 earnings will be released after the market closes on Thursday, May 1, 2025. Management will host a conference call on the following day, Friday, May 2, 2025, at 10:00 AM Central Time.

headline: Camden Property Trust Named One of Fortune’s 100 Best Companies to Work For®
summary: HOUSTON, April 02, 2025--Camden Property Trust (NYSE:CPT) (the "Company") announced today that it has been ranked 18th on Fortune’s 28th annual 100 Best Companies to Work For list. The full list and related stories will appear in the April/May issue of Fortune and can be accessed online now here.
